.nf

.B
new(Type) -> digraph()
.br
.fi
.br
.RS
.TP 3
Types:

Type = [\fBd_type()\fR\&]
.br
.nf
\fBd_type()\fR\& = \fBd_cyclicity()\fR\& | \fBd_protection()\fR\&
.fi
.br
.nf
\fBd_cyclicity()\fR\& = acyclic | cyclic
.fi
.br
.nf
\fBd_protection()\fR\& = private | protected
.fi
.br
.RE
.RS
.LP
Returns an \fBempty digraph\fR\& with properties according to the options in \fIType\fR\&:
.RS 2
.TP 2
.B
